    "description": "Copenhagen, the epitome of Nordic cool, combines cutting-edge design with centuries-old charm. The city's bicycle culture and commitment to sustainability create a unique urban rhythm, while the concept of 'hygge' (coziness) permeates its cafés and homes. From the colorful houses of Nyhavn to the minimalist lines of the Louisiana Museum, Copenhagen showcases Danish design excellence. The city's food scene ranges from traditional smørrebrød to Noma's innovative Nordic cuisine, and its harbor baths and urban parks reflect the Danish love for outdoor living.",
